title: Virtual Greeting
body_html:
Don't just gift things...

Add this product to your gift purchase, record a greeting with your cell phone and surprise the recipient.

Don't worry about the rest, the store will see that it arrives with your gift.

 

How does it work?

1

Add your surprise greeting from the cart.

2

Fill the fields From, To, Message.

3

You will be able to add an Audio, Photo or a Video.

The store will send a QR with your gift.
